docs/_build/
# docs/_generated/ contains per-tool stub .rst files written by
# docs/conf.py's _generate_tool_stubs() setup hook on every Sphinx
# build. They are derived from src/compiletools/README.ct-*.rst — the
# README is the source of truth, the stub is just an `.. include::`.
# Committing them would bake in a snapshot that drifts from the
# READMEs as new tools are added or renamed.
